# Resolve the shared contract package from GitHub Packages (see ADR 0006).
# Authenticate with a token that has `read:packages` for the UMGCCAPSTONE org,
# exposed as the NODE_AUTH_TOKEN environment variable. Do NOT commit a token.
#   - Local: set NODE_AUTH_TOKEN in your shell (or use a personal ~/.npmrc).
#   - CI: provide it via a secret (e.g. GITHUB_TOKEN / a PAT).
# The `@umgccapstone/contracts` dependency is added once the package is published;
# until then the app uses the local stub in src/types/contracts.
@umgccapstone:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com/
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${NODE_AUTH_TOKEN}
